- Do not infer decisions or commitments that were not explicitly stated
- Organize by themes, not chronologically
- Preserve key phrases and strategic terminology
- Quote exact numbers, dates, and commitments verbatim
- Stop when content is covered - no padding
- Short discussions = brief notes
- Use {{ config.general.summary_language | language }}
